LineSpeed.name: LineSpeed
LineSpeed.description: An indication of configured network line speed.

DuplexSetting.name: DuplexSetting
DuplexSetting.description: An indication of configured duplex mode.

AutoNegotiation.name: AutoNegotiation
AutoNegotiation.description: An indication of configured auto-negotiation mode.

EnabledOrNot.name: EnabledOrNot
EnabledOrNot.description: An indication of whether a feature is configured as enabled or disabled.

FailoverAction.name: FailoverAction
FailoverAction.description: An indication of whether a segment should pass traffic on failover.

LinkDownMode.name: LinkDownMode
LinkDownMode.description: An indication of configured link-down-synchronization mode.

portConfigTable.name: portConfigTable
portConfigTable.description: Table of slots/ports on the device and their configuration settings.

portConfigEntry.name: portConfigEntry
portConfigEntry.description: An entry in the slot/port table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

portConfigLineSpeed.name: portConfigLineSpeed
portConfigLineSpeed.description: The line speed configuration setting of this port.

portConfigDuplex.name: portConfigDuplex
portConfigDuplex.description: The duplex configuration setting of this port.

portConfigAutoNeg.name: portConfigAutoNeg
portConfigAutoNeg.description: The auto-negotiation configuration setting of this port.

portConfigShutdown.name: portConfigShutdown
portConfigShutdown.description: The shutdown configuration setting of this port. Shutdown enabled means that the port is manually removed from service. Shutdown disabled means that the port is free to come up normally.

portConfigLoopback.name: portConfigLoopback
portConfigLoopback.description: The loopback (on or off) configuration setting of this port.

portConfigFailover.name: portConfigFailover
portConfigFailover.description: The failover action (block or permit) configuration setting of this port.

portConfigLDSMode.name: portConfigLDSMode
portConfigLDSMode.description: The link-down sync mode (hub, breaker, or wire) setting of this port.

portConfigLDSTimeout.name: portConfigLDSTimeout
portConfigLDSTimeout.description: The link-down sync timeout configuration setting of this port.
